  - m_Id: 7000000000013
    m_Localized: Textile Workers Strike
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001001
    m_Localized: Escalating conflicts have sparked a global arms race. Prices are rising
      for small arms, heavy arms, munitions, and battle tanks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001002
    m_Localized: Technological advances and subsidies are fueling an auto boom. Prices
      are up for cars, engines, steel and iron ingots, aluminum, and crude oil.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001003
    m_Localized: Revolutionary aerospace designs are revitalizing the market. Fighter
      jets, aluminum, engines, and electronic components are rising in price.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001004
    m_Localized: Supply chain disruptions have halted semiconductor output. Electronic
      components, precision tools, and machine parts are rising in price.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001005
    m_Localized: A massive online sale has emptied warehouses. Electronics, basic and
      premium clothing, furniture, and simple tools are in record demand.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001006
    m_Localized: Economic instability is driving investors to safe havens. Gold ore
      and pure gold prices are climbing steeply.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001007
    m_Localized: Rapid urbanization has sparked a construction frenzy. Steel, machine
      parts, simple tools, wood logs, fine and premium wood, and basic and premium
      furniture prices are surging.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001008
    m_Localized: New sumptuary laws ban luxury sales in major markets. Premium clothing,
      premium furniture, and pure gold prices are falling.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001009
    m_Localized: Catastrophic mine failures have halted extraction. Coal, iron ore,
      copper ore and ingots, aluminum ore, and gold ore prices are surging.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001010
    m_Localized: Geopolitical conflicts in oil-producing regions have slashed output.
      Crude oil and coal prices are spiking.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001011
    m_Localized: Historic peace treaties are cutting military budgets worldwide. Small
      arms, heavy arms, munitions, battle tanks, and fighter jets are falling in
      price.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001012
    m_Localized: Heavy tariffs on imported metals have disrupted trade. Steel ingots,
      iron ingots, and iron ore prices are surging.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000001013
    m_Localized: Massive textile strikes have paralyzed factories. Fabric, basic clothing,
      and premium clothing prices are rising.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
